---
title: "Sign in with Google or Microsoft"
date: 2021-11-20T18:10:13Z
weight = 6
draft: false
---

Add a Google or Microsoft account to your Example.com username and you can sign in with these services.

{{% notice info "Information" %}}
At the moment, it is not possible to sign in with other services.
{{% /notice %}}

These instructions explain how to add a Google or Microsoft account.

1. Sign in with your Example.com username.
2. Select your profile > **Edit my account**.
3. Choose **Add/Remove Google or Microsoft**.
4. Choose the Google or Microsoft account you want to use.
5. Confirm your username and password.
6. Choose **Next**.
7. Choose **Done**.

